# Personal context for the MCP server. Copy to mcp_prompt.txt and edit.
# This is sent to the LLM at the start of every session, so it learns
# your shorthand, interests, and timezone without repeating yourself.
#
# Examples of what to put here:
#   - Topics you care about ("I follow AI policy and climate discourse")
#   - Shorthand you use ("when I say 'the discourse' I mean ...")
#   - Names or handles you refer to obliquely ("'the NYT guy' is @...")
